{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898222514,"sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc6b191001YFk1xY1FRuZG2d","messageID":"msg_d7bc6a6d5001leQbYlG94y7yOc","sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_e569b2f2b1104d73af1191b5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore project structure","prompt":"Explore the current working directory to understand the project structure. Look for:\n1. Any existing documentation or docs folder\n2. Any existing task files or checklists\n3. Package.json or similar config files\n4. Any existing Docusaurus configuration\n5. The overall project structure\n\nReturn a summary of what you find, including file paths and relevant configuration details.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_284394162ffelzIL84JV35pikP (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a comprehensive understanding of the project. Here is my summary:\n\n---\n\n## Project Structure Summary: AgentCube\n\n### Overview\n\n**AgentCube** is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents. It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic through session-aware proxies, and manages sandbox lifecycles.\n\n- **Go module**: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (Go 1.25.0)\n- **Python SDK/CLI**: Python >= 3.10\n- **Source repo**: `github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube`\n\n---\n\n### 1. Documentation / Docs Folder\n\n**Location**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/`\n\nThe `docs/` directory currently contains only **one file**:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/design.md` -- This is the design document for **AR-042: Docusaurus Documentation Site Framework**. It is a comprehensive 795-line design spec that describes the planned Docusaurus 3.x documentation site, including:\n  - Full directory structure (package.json, docusaurus.config.ts, sidebars.ts, src/, docs/, versioned_docs/, i18n/)\n  - Site configuration with i18n (en/zh), versioning, Algolia search, Mermaid diagrams\n  - Sidebar definitions, category metadata, frontmatter schema\n  - MDX component interfaces (ApiEndpoint, K8sResource)\n  - Error handling, testing strategy, CI/CD pipeline\n  - Initial content checklist (19 docs, all in \"Draft\" status)\n  - 5-phase implementation plan\n\n**Important**: The Docusaurus project has NOT been scaffolded yet. The `docs/` folder only contains the design document -- no `package.json`, no `docusaurus.config.ts`, no `sidebars.ts`, no actual documentation content.\n\n### 2. Task Files / Checklists\n\n**Root-level task file**:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md` -- Tasks for **AR-023: CLI invoke/status commands** (Python, 15 tasks with dependency graph)\n\n**Per-change task files** (42 change requests, AR-001 through AR-042):\n- Each `changes/AR-XXX/` folder contains: `tasks.md`, `design.md`, `proposal.md`, and some have `delta-spec.md`\n- Full list: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/` through `AR-042/`\n\n**Other markdown documentation at root level**:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md` -- Project context (purpose, tech stack, architecture, conventions)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` -- AR-040: Python SDK/CLI unit tests design\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md` -- Proposal document\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` -- Delta specification\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/test_spec.md` -- Test specification\n\n### 3. Package.json / Config Files\n\n**No `package.json` exists anywhere in the project.** The Docusaurus `package.json` has not been created yet.\n\n**Python config files**:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/python-sdk/pyproject.toml`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/pyproject.toml`\n\n**Go config**:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.mod` -- Module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`, Go 1.25.0\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/go.sum`\n\n**Build system**:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/Makefile` -- 195 lines with targets for: Go build (router, workloadmanager, agentd, picod), Docker, Helm, Python lint/test, code generation\n\n### 4. Docusaurus Configuration\n\n**No Docusaurus configuration exists yet.** There is no `docusaurus.config.ts`, no `sidebars.ts`, no `babel.config.js`, no `tsconfig.json` in the `docs/` folder.\n\nThe design document (`docs/design.md`) contains detailed **inline code examples** of what the configuration should look like, including:\n- `docusaurus.config.ts` with i18n (en/zh), versioning, Algolia search, Mermaid support\n- `sidebars.ts` with 7 categories: Getting Started, Architecture, User Guide, API Reference, Integrations, Operations, Contributing\n- `_category_.json` templates\n- Planned dependencies: `@docusaurus/core ^3.7.0`, `@docusaurus/preset-classic ^3.7.0`, React 19, etc.\n\n### 5. Overall Project Structure\n\n```\n[opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z]/\n|-- .github/workflows/              # GitHub Actions CI/CD\n|-- bin/                            # Compiled Go binaries\n|-- changes/                        # 42 AR folders (AR-001 to AR-042), each with tasks.md, design.md, proposal.md, delta-spec.md\n|-- ci-cd/                          # CI/CD design and spec\n|-- cli-toolkit/                    # CLI toolkit design and spec\n|-- client-go/                      # Go client library\n|-- cmd/                            # Go binaries + Python CLI\n|   |-- agentd/                     # Idle cleanup controller\n|   |-- cli/                        # Python CLI (pyproject.toml)\n|   |-- picod/                      # PicoD daemon\n|   |-- router/                     # HTTP router\n|   |-- workloadmanager/            # Workload manager\n|-- code-execution/                 # Code execution design and spec\n|-- deployment/                     # Deployment design and spec\n|-- docker/                         # Dockerfiles (Dockerfile, Dockerfile.router, Dockerfile.picod)\n|-- docs/                           # Docusaurus docs folder (currently only design.md)\n|-- example/                        # Example projects (pcap_analyzer)\n|-- hack/                           # Code generation scripts\n|-- idle-cleanup/                   # Idle cleanup design and spec\n|-- integrations/                   # Integration specs (dify-plugin)\n|-- manifests/                      # Helm charts (manifests/charts/base)\n|-- pkg/                            # Go packages\n|   |-- agentd/\n|   |-- apis/\n|   |-- common/\n|   |-- picod/\n|   |-- router/\n|   |-- store/\n|   |-- workloadmanager/\n|-- python-sdk/                     # Python SDK (pyproject.toml, tests/)\n|-- sandbox-orchestration/          # Sandbox orchestration design and spec\n|-- session-routing/                # Session routing design and spec\n|-- session-store/                  # Session store design and spec\n|-- testing/                        # Test manifests\n|-- go.mod / go.sum                 # Go module definition\n|-- Makefile                        # Build system\n|-- project.md                      # Project context\n|-- design.md                       # AR-040: Python SDK test design\n|-- proposal.md                     # Proposal document\n|-- tasks.md                        # AR-023: CLI tasks\n|-- delta-spec.md                   # Delta specification\n|-- test_spec.md                    # Test specification\n|-- coverage.out                    # Go coverage output\n```\n\n### Key Findings\n\n1. **The Docusaurus documentation site has NOT been implemented yet.** The `docs/` folder only contains a design specification (`design.md`). All configuration files (`package.json`, `docusaurus.config.ts`, `sidebars.ts`), source files (`src/`), and documentation content (`docs/intro.md`, etc.) need to be created.\n\n2. **The project follows an \"OpenSpec\" methodology** with 42 change requests (AR-001 through AR-042), each containing tasks, design, proposal, and delta-spec documents.\n\n3. **AR-042** is the specific change request for the Docusaurus documentation site. Its design document is thorough and provides all the configuration templates needed for implementation.\n\n4. **No `package.json` or Node.js dependencies exist** anywhere in the project -- the Docusaurus setup is entirely greenfield.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_284394162ffelzIL84JV35pikP","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore project structure","time":{"start":1775898115739,"end":1775898222511}}}}
