{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898228319,"sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc87185001azzwxqrZEJZv1P","messageID":"msg_d7bc85ffd001M8IBwdvHldbGof","sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_1be1617b3d854b3f9ec4d035","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-023 — CLI invoke/status 命令 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** cmd/cli\n4: > **Language:** Python\n5: > **Size:** M\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-023/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-023/design.md`, `changes/AR-023/delta-spec.md`\n8: > **Dependency:** AR-022 (publish command) — requires published agent endpoint\n9: \n10: ## T1. 实现 InvokeRuntime 类\n11: \n12: - [ ] 1.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py`\n13: - [ ] 1.2 定义 `InvokeRuntime` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n14: - [ ] 1.3 实现 `invoke(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n15:   - 加载 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n16:   - 校验 `agent_endpoint` 存在 → 否则 `ValueError`\n17:   - 发送 HTTP POST 请求到 endpoint\n18:   - 返回响应结果\n19: - [ ] 1.4 创建对应测试文件\n20: \n21: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_invoke_runtime.py -v` 全部通过\n22: \n23: ---\n24: \n25: ## T2. 增强 StatusRuntime 类\n26: \n27: - [ ] 2.1 修改 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py`\n28: - [ ] 2.2 实现 `status(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n29:   - 加载 `agent_metadata.yaml`\n30:   - 根据 `k8s_deployment.type` 路由到正确的状态查询\n31:   - 返回状态信息\n32: - [ ] 2.3 实现/增强 `_get_cr_k8s_status(self, metadata) -> Dict[str, Any]`\n33: - [ ] 2.4 创建对应测试文件\n34: \n35: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_status_runtime.py -v` 全部通过\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## T3. 实现 CLI invoke 命令入口\n40: \n41: - [ ] 3.1 在 `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` 中添加 `invoke` 命令\n42: - [ ] 3.2 选项：`workspace`, `prompt`, `verbose`\n43: - [ ] 3.3 命令体：调用 `InvokeRuntime.invoke()`，Rich 格式输出响应\n44: - [ ] 3.4 创建对应测试文件\n45: \n46: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_invoke_command.py -v` 全部通过\n47: \n48: ---\n49: \n50: ## T4. 实现 CLI status 命令入口\n51: \n52: - [ ] 4.1 在 `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` 中添加 `status` 命令\n53: - [ ] 4.2 选项：`workspace`, `verbose`\n54: - [ ] 4.3 命令体：调用 `StatusRuntime.status()`，Rich Table 格式输出状态\n55: - [ ] 4.4 创建对应测试文件\n56: \n57: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_status_command.py -v` 全部通过\n58: \n59: ---\n60: \n61: ## T5. 代码质量门禁与最终验证\n62: \n63: - [ ] 5.1 运行 `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认无 lint 错误\n64: - [ ] 5.2 运行 `ruff format --check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认格式合规\n65: - [ ] 5.3 运行 `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认无类型错误\n66: - [ ] 5.4 运行 `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v --cov=agentcube` 确认覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n67: - [ ] 5.5 运行 `kubectl-agentcube invoke --help` 确认帮助输出\n68: - [ ] 5.6 运行 `kubectl-agentcube status --help` 确认帮助输出\n69: \n70: **Verification:** 以上全部通过；exit code 均为 0\n71: \n72: ---\n73: \n74: ## Task Dependencies\n75: \n76: ```\n77: T1 (InvokeRuntime) ───────────────────────────────┐\n78:                                                    │\n79: T2 (StatusRuntime) ────────────────────────────────┤\n80:                                                    │\n81: T3 (CLI invoke 命令) ←── T1 ───────────────────────┤\n82:                                                    │\n83: T4 (CLI status 命令) ←── T2 ───────────────────────┤\n84:                                                    │\n85: T5 (质量门禁) ←── T3, T4 ──────────────────────────┘\n86: ```\n87: \n88: **Parallel execution:**\n89: - T1 和 T2 可并行开发\n90: - T3 需 T1 完成后开始\n91: - T4 需 T2 完成后开始\n92: - T3 和 T4 可并行开发\n93: - T5 需所有前置任务完成\n94: \n95: ---\n96: \n97: ## Acceptance Criteria\n98: \n99: | # | Criterion | Command |\n100: |---|-----