{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898231613,"sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc87fb3001CwjJTnoWgPmVlk","messageID":"msg_d7bc876900016I51FPSW8YM6Wv","sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_29d80802cc5a49e294b375bb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-042: Docusaurus 文档站框架 — Design\n2: \n3: ## 1. Architecture\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 Purpose\n6: \n7: This AR establishes a Docusaurus 3.x documentation site for AgentCube, providing versioned documentation, multi-language support (en/zh), search, and automated CI/CD deployment. The docs site serves as the primary developer and user-facing documentation for the Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform.\n8: \n9: ### 1.2 Scope\n10: \n11: | Component | Description | Status |\n12: |-----------|-------------|--------|\n13: | Docusaurus 3.x project scaffold | `docs/` directory with full site configuration | **New** |\n14: | Documentation content structure | Organized docs by audience and topic | **New** |\n15: | Versioned documentation | Docusaurus versioning for release docs | **New** |\n16: | Multi-language (i18n) | English + Simplified Chinese | **New** |\n17: | Search integration | Algolia DocSearch or local search | **New** |\n18: | CI/CD deployment | GitHub Pages or custom domain via GitHub Actions | **New** |\n19: | Custom theme configuration | AgentCube branding, colors, logo | **New** |\n20: | MDX support | Interactive docs with React components | **New** |\n21: \n22: ### 1.3 System Context\n23: \n24: ```\n25: ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n26: │                    Docusaurus 3.x Site                        │\n27: │                                                                │\n28: │  ┌────────────┐  ┌────────────┐  ┌────────────────────────┐  │\n29: │  │  Markdown  │  │    MDX     │  │   React Components     │  │\n30: │  │  /docs/    │  │  (inline)  │  │   /src/components/     │  │\n31: │  └─────┬──────┘  └─────┬──────┘  └──────────┬─────────────┘  │\n32: │        │               │                     │                 │\n33: │  ┌─────▼───────────────▼─────────────────────▼─────────────┐  │\n34: │  │              Docusaurus Build Pipeline                    │  │\n35: │  │         (webpack/babel → static HTML/JS/CSS)             │  │\n36: │  └────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────┘  │\n37: │                           │                                    │\n38: │  ┌────────────────────────▼────────────────────────────────┐  │\n39: │  │              Static Output (build/)                       │  │\n40: │  └────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────┘  │\n41: └───────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────┘\n42:                             │\n43:                             ▼\n44:               ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n45:               │   GitHub Pages / CDN        │\n46:               │   (docs.agentcube.dev)      │\n47:               └─────────────────────────────┘\n48:                             │\n49:                             ▼\n50:               ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n51:               │   End Users / Developers    │\n52:               └─────────────────────────────┘\n53: ```\n54: \n55: ### 1.4 Design Principles\n56: \n57: - **Docs-as-code**: Documentation lives in the same repository, reviewed via PRs, versioned with releases.\n58: - **Progressive disclosure**: Quick start for new users, deep dives for advanced operators.\n59: - **Version-aligned**: Documentation versions track AgentCube release tags (v0.x, v1.x, etc.).\n60: - **Bilingual by default**: All content authored in English with Chinese translations; fallback to English for untranslated pages.\n61: - **Searchable**: Full-text search across all versions and languages.\n62: \n63: ### 1.5 Directory Structure\n64: \n65: ```\n66: docs/\n67: ├── package.json                          # Node.js dependencies\n68: ├── docusaurus.config.ts                  # Site configuration (TypeScript)\n69: ├── sidebars.ts                           # Sidebar navigation definitions\n70: ├── babel.config.js                       # Babel config (if needed)\n71: ├── tsconfig.json                         # TypeScript configuration\n72: ├── src/\n73: │   ├── css/\n74: │   │   └── custom.css                   # Global CSS overrides\n75: │   ├── components/\n76: │   │   ├── HomepageFeatures/\n77: │   │   │   ├── index.tsx\n78: │   │   │   └── styles.module.css\n79: │   │   ├── ApiEndpoint/                  # MDX component for API docs\n80: │   │   │   └── index.tsx\n81: │   │   └── K8sResource/                  # MDX component for CRD docs\n82: │   │       └── index.tsx\n83: │   ├── pages/\n84: │   │   ├── index.tsx                    # Landing page\n85: │   │   ├── index.module.css\n86: │   │   └── markdown-page.md\n87: │   └── theme/                            # Swizzled theme components\n88: │       ├── Footer/\n89: │       │   └── index.tsx\n90: │       └── Navbar/\n91: │           └── Logo/\n92: │               └── index.tsx\n93: ├── docs/\n94: │   ├── intro.md                          # Introduction / Overview\n95: │   ├── getting-started/\n96: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n97: │   │   ├── installation.md\n98: │   │   ├── quick-start.md\n99: │   │   └── configuration.md\n100: │   ├── architecture/\n101: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n102: │   │   ├── overview.md\n103: │   │   ├── components.md\n104: │   │   ├── session-routing.md\n105: │   │   └── sandbox-lifecycle.md\n106: │   ├── user-guide/\n107: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n108: │   │   ├── code-interpreter.md\n109: │   │   ├── agent-runtime.md\n110: │   │   ├── cli.md\n111: │   │   └── python-sdk.md\n112: │   ├── api-reference/\n113: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n114: │   │   ├── control-plane.md\n115: │   │   ├── data-plane.md\n116: │   │   └── crds.md\n117: │   ├── integrations/\n118: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n119: │   │   ├── dify-plugin.md\n120: │   │   └── langchain.md\n121: │   ├── operations/\n122: │   │   ├── _category_.json\n123: │   │   ├── deployment.md\n124: │   │   ├── monitoring.md\n125: │   │   ├── troubleshooting.md\n126: │   │   └── security.md\n127: │   └── contributing/\n128: │       ├── _category_.json\n129: │       ├── development.md\n130: │       ├── testing.md\n131: │       └── release-process.md\n132: ├── versioned_docs/\n133: │   └── version-0.1.x/                    # Auto-generated by docusaurus docs:version\n134: │       └── ...                           # Snapshot of docs at release time\n135: ├── versioned_sidebars/\n136: │   └── version-0.1.x-sidebars.json       # Sidebar snapshot per version\n137: ├── versions.json                         # List of available versions\n138: └── i18n/\n139:     └── zh/\n140:         ├── docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/\n141:         │   ├── current/                  # Translated docs (mirrors docs/)\n142:         │   │   ├── intro.md\n143:         │   │   ├── getting-started/\n144:         │   │   ├── architecture/\n145:         │   │   └── ...\n146:         │   └── current.json              # Category/label translations\n147:         ├── docusaurus-theme-classic/\n148:         │   ├── navbar.json               # Navbar label translations\n149:         │   └── footer.json               # Footer label translations\n150:         └── code.json                     # UI string translations\n151: ```\n152: \n153: ### 1.6 Dependencies\n154: \n155: | Dependency | Version | Purpose |\n156: |------------|---------|---------|\n157: | `@docusaurus/core` | ^3.7.0 | Core framework |\n158: | `@docusaurus/preset-classic` | ^3.7.0 | Classic theme (docs, blog, pages) |\n159: | `@docusaurus/module-type-aliases` | ^3.7.0 | TypeScript type aliases |\n160: | `@docusaurus/tsconfig` | ^3.7.0 | TypeScript base config |\n161: | `@docusaurus/types` | ^3.7.0 | TypeScript types |\n162: | `@mdx-js/react` | ^3.0.0 | MDX rendering |\n163: | `clsx` | ^2.0.0 | Conditional CSS class utility |\n164: | `prism-react-renderer` | ^2.3.0 | Code block syntax highlighting |\n165: | `react` | ^19.0.0 | UI framework |\n166: | `react-dom` | ^19.0.0 | DOM rendering |\n167: | `@docusaurus/plugin-client-redirects` | ^3.7.0 | Redirect rules (optional) |\n168: | `@docusaurus/plugin-ideal-image` | ^3.7.0 | Responsive images (optional) |\n169: | `@easyops-cn/docusaurus-search-local` | ^0.48.0 | Local search (fallback for DocSearch) |\n170: \n171: ## 2. Data Structures\n172: \n173: ### 2.1 Site Configuration (`docusaurus.config.ts`)\n174: \n175: ```typescript\n176: import { themes as prismThemes } from 'prism-react-renderer';\n177: import type { Config } from '@docusaurus/types';\n178: import type * as Preset from '@docusaurus/preset-classic';\n179: \n180: const config: Config = {\n181:   title: 'AgentCube',\n182:   tagline: 'Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agents',\n183:   favicon: 'img/favicon.ico',\n184:   url: 'https://docs.agentcube.dev',\n185:   baseUrl: '/',\n186:   organizationName: 'volcano-sh',\n187:   projectName: 'agentcube',\n188:   deploymentBranch: 'gh-pages',\n189: \n190:   i18n: {\n191:     defaultLocale: 'en',\n192:     locales: ['en', 'zh'],\n193:     localeConfigs: {\n194:       en: { label: 'English', direction: 'ltr' },\n195:       zh: { label: '简体中文', direction: 'ltr' },\n196:     },\n197:   },\n198: \n199:   presets: [\n200:     [\n201:       'classic',\n202:       {\n203:         docs: {\n204:           sidebarPath: './sidebars.ts',\n205:           editUrl: 'https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/tree/main/docs/',\n206:           showLastUpdateAuthor: true,\n207:           showLastUpdateTime: true,\n208:           lastVersion: 'current',\n209:           versions: {\n210:             current: {\n211:               label: 'Next 🚧',\n212:               path: 'next',\n213:               badge: true,\n214:             },\n215:           },\n216:         },\n217:         blog: {\n218:           showReadingTime: true,\n219:           editUrl: 'https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/tree/main/docs/',\n220:         },\n221:         theme: {\n222:           customCss: './src/css/custom.css',\n223:         },\n224:       } satisfies Preset.Options,\n225:     ],\n226:   ],\n227: \n228:   themeConfig: {\n229:     image: 'img/agentcube-social-card.png',\n230:     navbar: {\n231:       title: 'AgentCube',\n232:       logo: { alt: 'AgentCube Logo', src: 'img/logo.svg' },\n233:       items: [\n234:         { type: 'docSidebar', sidebarId: 'tutorialSidebar', position: 'left', label: 'Docs' },\n235:         { to: '/blog', label: 'Blog', position: 'left' },\n236:         { type: 'docsVersionDropdown', position: 'right' },\n237:         { type: 'localeDropdown', position: 'right' },\n238:         {\n239:           href: 'https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube',\n240:           label: 'GitHub',\n241:           position: 'right',\n242:         },\n243:       ],\n244:     },\n245:     footer: {\n246:       style: 'dark',\n247:       links: [\n248:         {\n249:           title: 'Docs',\n250:           items: [\n251:             { label: 'Getting Started', to: '/docs/getting-started/quick-start' },\n252:             { label: 'Architecture', to: '/docs/architecture/overview' },\n253:             { label: 'API Reference', to: '/docs/api-reference/control-plane' },\n254:           ],\n255:         },\n256:         {\n257:           title: 'Community',\n258:           items: [\n259:             { label: 'GitHub Discussions', href: 'https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/discussions' },\n260:             { label: 'Slack', href: 'https://kubernetes.slack.com/' },\n261:           ],\n262:         },\n263:         {\n264:           title: 'More',\n265:           items: [\n266:             { label: 'Blog', to: '/blog' },\n267:             { label: 'GitHub', href: 'https://github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube' },\n268:           ],\n269:         },\n270:       ],\n271:       copyright: `Copyright © ${new Date().getFullYear()} The AgentCube Authors. Built with Docusaurus.`,\n272:     },\n273:     prism: {\n274:       theme: prismThemes.github,\n275:       darkTheme: prismThemes.dracula,\n276:       additionalLanguages: ['bash', 'go', 'python', 'yaml', 'json', 'docker', 'kubernetes'],\n277:     },\n278:     algolia: {\n279:       appId: 'TBD',\n280:       apiKey: 'TBD',\n281:       indexName: 'agentcube',\n282:       contextualSearch: true,\n283:     },\n284:   } satisfies Preset.ThemeConfig,\n285: \n286:   markdown: {\n287:     mermaid: true,\n288:   },\n289:   themes: ['@docusaurus/theme-mermaid'],\n290: };\n291: \n292: export default config;\n293: ```\n294: \n295: ### 2.2 Sidebar Definition (`sidebars.ts`)\n296: \n297: ```typescript\n298: import type { SidebarsConfig } from '@docusaurus/plugin-content-docs';\n299: \n300: const sidebars: SidebarsConfig = {\n301:   tutorialSidebar: [\n302:     'intro',\n303:     {\n304:       type: 'category',\n305:       label: 'Getting Started',\n306:       link: { type: 'doc', id: 'getting-started/installation' },\n307:       items: [\n308:         'getting-started/installation',\n309:         'getting-started/quick-start',\n310:         'getting-started/configuration',\n311:       ],\n312:     },\n313:     {\n314:       type: 'category',\n315:       label: 'Architecture',\n316:       link: { type: 'doc', id: 'architecture/overview' },\n317:       items: [\n318:         'architecture/overview',\n319:         'architecture/components',\n320:         'architecture/session-routing',\n321:         'architecture/sandbox-lifecycle',\n322:       ],\n323:     },\n324:     {\n325:       type: 'category',\n326:       label: 'User Guide',\n327:       link: { type: 'doc', id: 'user-guide/code-interpreter' },\n328:       items: [\n329:         'user-guide/code-interpreter',\n330:         'user-guide/agent-runtime',\n331:         'user-guide/cli',\n332:         'user-guide/python-sdk',\n333:       ],\n334:     },\n335:     {\n336:       type: 'category',\n337:       label: 'API Reference',\n338:       link: { type: 'doc', id: 'api-reference/control-plane' },\n339:       items: [\n340:         'api-reference/control-plane',\n341:         'api-reference/data-plane',\n342:         'api-reference/crds',\n343:       ],\n344:     },\n345:     {\n346:       type: 'category',\n347:       label: 'Integrations',\n348:       link: { type: 'doc', id: 'integrations/dify-plugin' },\n349:       items: [\n350:         'integrations/dify-plugin',\n351:         'integrations/langchain',\n352:       ],\n353:     },\n354:     {\n355:       type: 'category',\n356:       label: 'Operations',\n357:       link: { type: 'doc', id: 'operations/deployment' },\n358:       items: [\n359:         'operations/deployment',\n360:         'operations/monitoring',\n361:         'operations/troubleshooting',\n362:         'operations/security',\n363:       ],\n364:     },\n365:     {\n366:       type: 'category',\n367:       label: 'Contributing',\n368:       link: { type: 'doc', id: 'contributing/development' },\n369:       items: [\n370:         'contributing/development',\n371:         'contributing/testing',\n372:         'contributing/release-process',\n373:       ],\n374:     },\n375:   ],\n376: };\n377: \n378: export default sidebars;\n379: ```\n380: \n381: ### 2.3 Category Metadata (`_category_.json`)\n382: \n383: Each documentation category directory contains a `_category_.json` file:\n384: \n385: ```json\n386: {\n387:   \"label\": \"Getting Started\",\n388:   \"position\": 2,\n389:   \"link\": {\n390:     \"type\": \"generated-index\",\n391:     \"description\": \"Learn how to install and get started with AgentCube.\"\n392:   }\n393: }\n394: ```\n395: \n396: ### 2.4 Frontmatter Schema\n397: \n398: All `.md` and `.mdx` files use YAML frontmatter:\n399: \n400: ```yaml\n401: ---\n402: sidebar_position: 1\n403: title: Quick Start\n404: description: Get AgentCube running in 5 minutes\n405: keywords: [quickstart, installation, kubernetes]\n406: ---\n407: ```\n408: \n409: | Field | Type | Required | Description |\n410: |-------|------|----------|-------------|\n411: | `sidebar_position` | number | No | Order in sidebar (lower = first) |\n412: | `title` | string | No | Page title (defaults to filename) |\n413: | `description` | string | No | Meta description for SEO |\n414: | `keywords` | string[] | No | SEO keywords |\n415: | `slug` | string | No | Custom URL path override |\n416: | `hide_title` | boolean | No | Hide auto-generated title |\n417: | `sidebar_label` | string | No | Short label for sidebar |\n418: \n419: ### 2.5 MDX Component Interfaces\n420: \n421: #### `ApiEndpoint` — API endpoint documentation block\n422: \n423: ```tsx\n424: interface ApiEndpointProps {\n425:   method: 'GET' | 'POST' | 'PUT' | 'DELETE' | 'PATCH';\n426:   path: string;\n427:   description: string;\n428:   auth?: 'none' | 'bearer' | 'mtls';\n429: }\n430: ```\n431: \n432: #### `K8sResource` — Kubernetes CRD documentation block\n433: \n434: ```tsx\n435: interface K8sResourceProps {\n436:   group: string;\n437:   version: string;\n438:   kind: string;\n439:   scope: 'Namespaced' | 'Cluster';\n440:   yamlExample?: string;\n441: }\n442: ```\n443: \n444: ### 2.6 Version Metadata (`versions.json`)\n445: \n446: ```json\n447: [\"current\", \"0.1.x\"]\n448: ```\n449: \n450: Managed by `docusaurus docs:version 0.1.x` command. Each release creates a snapshot of the current docs.\n451: \n452: ## 3. API Contracts\n453: \n454: ### 3.1 Internal APIs (Docusaurus Plugin Contracts)\n455: \n456: Docusaurus does not expose external APIs; instead it defines plugin/preset contracts:\n457: \n458: | Contract | Type | Description |\n459: |----------|------|-------------|\n460: | `@docusaurus/plugin-content-docs` | Plugin | Processes `/docs/` markdown, builds sidebar, generates pages |\n461: | `@docusaurus/preset-classic` | Preset | Bundles docs, blog, pages, theme-classic |\n462: | `@docusaurus/theme-classic` | Theme | Provides default UI components (navbar, footer, sidebar) |\n463: \n464: ### 3.2 External Integration Points\n465: \n466: | Integration | Configuration | Purpose |\n467: |-------------|---------------|---------|\n468: | Algolia DocSearch | `themeConfig.algolia` | Full-text search across docs |\n469: | GitHub Edit URL | `presets[0][1].docs.editUrl` | \"Edit this page\" links to GitHub |\n470: | GitHub Pages | `organizationName`, `projectName`, `deploymentBranch` | `npm run deploy` pushes to gh-pages |\n471: | Google Analytics | `themeConfig.algolia` or custom plugin | Usage analytics (optional) |\n472: \n473: ### 3.3 Build Output Contract\n474: \n475: ```\n476: build/\n477: ├── index.html                    # Landing page\n478: ├── docs/\n479: │   ├── intro/\n480: │   │   └── index.html\n481: │   ├── getting-started/\n482: │   │   ├── installation/\n483: │   │   ├── quick-start/\n484: │   │   └── configuration/\n485: │   ├── next/                     # \"current\" versioned docs\n486: │   │   └── ...\n487: │   └── version-0.1.x/\n488: │       └── ...\n489: ├── zh/                           # Chinese locale\n490: │   └── docs/\n491: │       └── ...\n492: ├── blog/\n493: │   └── ...\n494: ├── assets/\n495: │   ├── js/\n496: │   ├── css/\n497: │   └── images/\n498: └── 404.html                      # Custom 404 page\n499: ```\n500: \n501: ### 3.4 URL Routing Contract\n502: \n503: | Pattern | Resolution |\n504: |---------|-----------|\n505: | `/docs/<id>` | Maps to `docs/<id>.md` |\n506: | `/docs/<version>/<id>` | Maps to `versioned_docs/version-<version>/<id>.md` |\n507: | `/<locale>/docs/<id>` | Maps to `i18n/<locale>/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/<id>.md` |\n508: | `/blog/<slug>` | Maps to `blog/<slug>.md` |\n509: | `/<path>` | Maps to `src/pages/<path>.tsx` or `src/pages/<path>/index.tsx` |\n510: \n511: ## 4. Error Handling\n512: \n513: ### 4.1 Build-Time Errors\n514: \n515: | Error | Cause | Handling |\n516: |-------|-------|----------|\n517: | Missing sidebar reference | `sidebars.ts` references non-existent doc ID | Build fails with clear error: `Doc sidebar item \"x\" references a non-existent doc` |\n518: | Broken internal link | Markdown link to non-existent doc | Build warning (configurable to error via `onBrokenMarkdownLinks: 'throw'`) |\n519: | Broken image reference | Image path does not exist | Build warning (configurable via `onBrokenAssets: 'throw'`) |\n520: | Invalid frontmatter | Malformed YAML frontmatter | Build fails with YAML parse error |\n521: | MDX syntax error | Invalid JSX in `.mdx` file | Build fails with JSX compilation error |\n522: | Duplicate doc ID | Two files with same inferred ID | Build fails with duplicate ID error |\n523: | Missing translation | i18n locale missing a translated doc | Falls back to default locale (English) with console warning |\n524: \n525: ### 4.2 Runtime Errors (Client-Side)\n526: \n527: | Error | Cause | Handling |\n528: |-------|-------|----------|\n529: | 404 page not found | User navigates to non-existent route | Custom 404 page with search and navigation links |\n530: | Search index unavailable | Algolia API key invalid or network error | Graceful degradation: search box shows \"Search unavailable\" |\n531: | Code block syntax error | Unsupported language in code fence | Prism falls back to plain text rendering |\n532: | Theme component error | Swizzled component throws error | React error boundary catches; shows fallback UI |\n533: \n534: ### 4.3 CI/CD Errors\n535: \n536: | Error | Cause | Handling |\n537: |-------|-------|----------|\n538: | `npm run build` fails | Build-time error (see 4.1) | CI fails; PR blocked from merging |\n539: | Deploy authentication failure | GitHub token missing or expired | CI fails; requires secret rotation |\n540: | Branch protection | gh-pages branch protected | CI fails; requires branch config change |\n541: \n542: ### 4.4 Error Configuration\n543: \n544: ```typescript\n545: // docusaurus.config.ts — strict mode for CI\n546: const config: Config = {\n547:   onBrokenLinks: 'throw',       // Fail build on broken links\n548:   onBrokenMarkdownLinks: 'warn', // Warn on broken markdown links\n549:   onBrokenAssets: 'throw',       // Fail build on missing images\n550:   onDuplicateRoutes: 'throw',    // Fail build on duplicate routes\n551:   // ...\n552: };\n553: ```\n554: \n555: ## 5. Testing Strategy\n556: \n557: ### 5.1 Test Categories\n558: \n559: | Category | Scope | Tool | Frequency |\n560: |----------|-------|------|-----------|\n561: | Build validation | `npm run build` succeeds with no errors | Docusaurus CLI | Every PR |\n562: | Link checking | No broken internal/external links | `docusaurus-mdx-checker` or `check-links` | Every PR |\n563: | Visual regression | UI matches expected rendering | Playwright / Percy | On demand |\n564: | Accessibility | WCAG 2.1 AA compliance | axe-core, Lighthouse CI | Every PR |\n565: | Performance | Lighthouse scores ≥ 90 | Lighthouse CI | Every PR |\n566: | i18n completeness | All zh translations present | Custom script | Weekly |\n567: | SEO validation | Meta tags, Open Graph, structured data | Custom script | Every PR |\n568: \n569: ### 5.2 Build Validation\n570: \n571: ```bash\n572: # Install dependencies\n573: cd docs && npm install\n574: \n575: # Type check\n576: npx tsc --noEmit\n577: \n578: # Build (static site generation)\n579: npm run build\n580: \n581: # Serve locally for manual verification\n582: npm run serve\n583: ```\n584: \n585: ### 5.3 Link Checking\n586: \n587: ```bash\n588: # Check for broken links in built output\n589: npx check-links build/**/*.html\n590: \n591: # Docusaurus built-in broken link detection (during build)\n592: # Configured via onBrokenLinks: 'throw' in docusaurus.config.ts\n593: ```\n594: \n595: ### 5.4 Lighthouse CI Configuration\n596: \n597: ```json\n598: {\n599:   \"ci\": {\n600:     \"collect\": {\n601:       \"staticDistDir\": \"./build\",\n602:       \"settings\": {\n603:         \"preset\": \"desktop\"\n604:       }\n605:     },\n606:     \"assert\": {\n607:       \"assertions\": {\n608:         \"categories:performance\": [\"warn\", { \"minScore\": 0.9 }],\n609:         \"categories:accessibility\": [\"error\", { \"minScore\": 0.95 }],\n610:         \"categories:best-practices\": [\"warn\", { \"minScore\": 0.9 }],\n611:         \"categories:seo\": [\"error\", { \"minScore\": 0.9 }]\n612:       }\n613:     }\n614:   }\n615: }\n616: ```\n617: \n618: ### 5.5 i18n Completeness Check\n619: \n620: ```bash\n621: #!/bin/bash\n622: # scripts/check-i18n.sh — compare en and zh doc file counts\n623: EN_COUNT=$(find docs/docs -name \"*.md\" -o -name \"*.mdx\" | wc -l)\n624: ZH_COUNT=$(find docs/i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current -name \"*.md\" -o -name \"*.mdx\" | wc -l)\n625: COVERAGE=$(echo \"scale=1; $ZH_COUNT * 100 / $EN_COUNT\" | bc)\n626: echo \"Chinese translation coverage: ${COVERAGE}%\"\n627: if (( $(echo \"$COVERAGE < 80\" | bc -l) )); then\n628:   echo \"WARNING: Translation coverage below 80%\"\n629:   exit 1\n630: fi\n631: ```\n632: \n633: ### 5.6 Test Execution\n634: \n635: ```bash\n636: # Full test suite\n637: cd docs && npm run build && npm run check-links && npm run check-i18n\n638: \n639: # Development server with hot reload\n640: cd docs && npm start\n641: \n642: # Type checking\n643: cd docs && npx tsc --noEmit\n644: \n645: # Production build\n646: cd docs && NODE_ENV=production npm run build\n647: \n648: # Preview production build locally\n649: cd docs && npm run serve -- --build --port 3000\n650: ```\n651: \n652: ### 5.7 CI Pipeline for Docs\n653: \n654: ```yaml\n655: # .github/workflows/docs.yml\n656: name: Docs CI\n657: \n658: on:\n659:   pull_request:\n660:     paths:\n661:       - 'docs/**'\n662:       - '.github/workflows/docs.yml'\n663: \n664: jobs:\n665:   build:\n666:     runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n667:     defaults:\n668:       run:\n669:         working-directory: docs\n670:     steps:\n671:       - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n672:       - uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n673:         with:\n674:           node-version: '20'\n675:           cache: 'npm'\n676:           cache-dependency-path: docs/package-lock.json\n677:       - run: npm ci\n678:       - run: npx tsc --noEmit\n679:       - run: npm run build\n680:       - name: Check links\n681:         run: npx check-links build/**/*.html --timeout 10000\n682:       - name: Check i18n coverage\n683:         run: bash ../scripts/check-i18n.sh\n684:       - name: Upload build artifact\n685:         if: success()\n686:         uses: actions/upload-pages-artifact@v3\n687:         with:\n688:           path: docs/build\n689: \n690:   deploy:\n691:     needs: build\n692:     if: github.ref == 'refs/heads/main'\n693:     runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n694:     permissions:\n695:       pages: write\n696:       id-token: write\n697:     environment:\n698:       name: github-pages\n699:       url: ${{ steps.deployment.outputs.page_url }}\n700:     steps:\n701:       - name: Deploy to GitHub Pages\n702:         id: deployment\n703:         uses: actions/deploy-pages@v4\n704: ```\n705: \n706: ### 5.8 Coverage Targets\n707: \n708: | Metric | Target |\n709: |--------|--------|\n710: | Build success rate | 100% |\n711: | Broken links | 0 |\n712: | i18n coverage (zh) | ≥ 80% |\n713: | Lighthouse Performance | ≥ 90 |\n714: | Lighthouse Accessibility | ≥ 95 |\n715: | Lighthouse SEO | ≥ 90 |\n716: | Lighthouse Best Practices | ≥ 90 |\n717: \n718: ### 5.9 Risk Areas\n719: \n720: | Risk | Mitigation |\n721: |------|-----------|\n722: | Docusaurus major version upgrade breaks config | Pin `^3.7.0` (minor updates only); test upgrade in separate branch |\n723: | Algolia DocSearch index not approved | Use `@easyops-cn/docusaurus-search-local` as fallback |\n724: | Large doc set causes slow builds | Use incremental builds; cache `node_modules` and `.docusaurus` |\n725: | Translation drift (en updated, zh stale) | Weekly i18n coverage check; automated Slack notification |\n726: | GitHub Pages rate limits | Use CDN (Cloudflare) in front of GitHub Pages for production |\n727: | MDX component breaking changes | Unit test custom components; pin React version |\n728: | Versioned docs diverge from current | Enforce `docusaurus docs:version` on each release tag |\n729: \n730: ### 5.10 Initial Content Checklist\n731: \n732: | Doc | Status | Priority |\n733: |-----|--------|----------|\n734: | `intro.md` — Project overview | **Draft** | P0 |\n735: | `getting-started/installation.md` — Helm install guide | **Draft** | P0 |\n736: | `getting-started/quick-start.md` — 5-minute tutorial | **Draft** | P0 |\n737: | `getting-started/configuration.md` — Helm values reference | **Draft** | P1 |\n738: | `architecture/overview.md` — System architecture | **Draft** | P0 |\n739: | `architecture/components.md` — Component deep dive | **Draft** | P1 |\n740: | `architecture/session-routing.md` — Router + session management | **Draft** | P1 |\n741: | `architecture/sandbox-lifecycle.md` — Sandbox creation to cleanup | **Draft** | P1 |\n742: | `user-guide/code-interpreter.md` — Code Interpreter usage | **Draft** | P0 |\n743: | `user-guide/agent-runtime.md` — Agent Runtime usage | **Draft** | P0 |\n744: | `user-guide/cli.md` — CLI commands reference | **Draft** | P1 |\n745: | `user-guide/python-sdk.md` — Python SDK reference | **Draft** | P1 |\n746: | `api-reference/control-plane.md` — Workload Manager API | **Draft** | P2 |\n747: | `api-reference/data-plane.md` — Router API | **Draft** | P2 |\n748: | `api-reference/crds.md` — CRD reference | **Draft** | P2 |\n749: | `operations/deployment.md` — Production deployment guide | **Draft** | P1 |\n750: | `operations/monitoring.md` — Metrics and alerts | **Draft** | P2 |\n751: | `operations/troubleshooting.md` — Common issues | **Draft** | P1 |\n752: | `operations/security.md` — Auth, RBAC, network policies | **Draft** | P1 |\n753: \n754: ## 6. Implementation Plan\n755: \n756: ### Phase 1: Scaffold (Week 1)\n757: \n758: - [ ] Initialize Docusaurus project in `docs/` directory\n759: - [ ] Configure `docusaurus.config.ts` with AgentCube branding\n760: - [ ] Set up sidebar structure (`sidebars.ts`)\n761: - [ ] Create category directories with `_category_.json` files\n762: - [ ] Add custom CSS theme (`src/css/custom.css`)\n763: - [ ] Configure TypeScript (`tsconfig.json`)\n764: - [ ] Add Mermaid diagram support\n765: \n766: ### Phase 2: Content Migration (Week 1-2)\n767: \n768: - [ ] Write `intro.md` from `project.md`\n769: - [ ] Migrate architecture docs from existing `design.md` files\n770: - [ ] Write getting-started guides (installation, quick-start)\n771: - [ ] Create user guide stubs for Code Interpreter, Agent Runtime, CLI, SDK\n772: - [ ] Add API reference skeletons\n773: \n774: ### Phase 3: i18n Setup (Week 2)\n775: \n776: - [ ] Initialize Chinese locale (`docusaurus write-translations --locale zh`)\n777: - [ ] Translate intro and getting-started docs\n778: - [ ] Set up translation workflow documentation\n779: - [ ] Add i18n coverage check script\n780: \n781: ### Phase 4: CI/CD (Week 2-3)\n782: \n783: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/docs.yml`\n784: - [ ] Configure GitHub Pages deployment\n785: - [ ] Add Lighthouse CI checks\n786: - [ ] Add link checking to PR pipeline\n787: - [ ] Configure custom domain (optional)\n788: \n789: ### Phase 5: Polish (Week 3)\n790: \n791: - [ ] Add custom MDX components (`ApiEndpoint`, `K8sResource`)\n792: - [ ] Configure Algolia DocSearch (apply for indexing)\n793: - [ ] Set up local search fallback\n794: - [ ] Add versioned docs for first release\n795: - [ ] Performance optimization (image compression, code splitting)\n\n(End of file - total 795 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-042: Docusaurus 文档站框架 — Design\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Purpose\n\nThis AR establishes a Docusaurus 3.x documentation site for AgentCube, providing versioned documentation, multi-language support (en/zh), search, and automated CI/CD deployment. The docs site serves as the primary developer and user-facing documentation for the Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform.\n\n### 1.2 Scope\n\n| Component | Description | Status |\n|-----------|-------------|--------|\n| Docusaurus 3.x project scaffold | `docs/` directory with full site configuration | **New** |\n| Documentation content structure | Organized docs by audience and topic | **New** |\n| Versioned documentation | Docusaurus versioning for release docs | **New** |\n| Multi-language (i18n) | English + Simplified Chinese | **New** |\n| Search integration | Algolia DocSearch or local search | **New** |\n| CI/CD deployment | GitHub Pages or custom domain via GitHub Actions | **New** |\n| Custom theme configuration | AgentCube branding, colors, logo | **New** |\n| MDX support | Interactive docs with React components | **New** |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/docs/design.md","time":{"start":1775898231604,"end":1775898231610}}}}
{"type":"step_finish","timestamp":1775898231673,"sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc8836c001i3OUDck0CTkvHY","reason":"tool-calls","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","messageID":"msg_d7bc876900016I51FPSW8YM6Wv","sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","type":"step-finish","tokens":{"total":20621,"input":20507,"output":71,"reasoning":43,"cache":{"write":0,"read":0}},"cost":0.005848146}}
{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775898233399,"sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc88a35001iHCh1seGvnjnbe","messageID":"msg_d7bc8838e001blADQCbz8sjLEY","sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775898306483,"sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","part":{"id":"prt_d7bc89074001Uu6VT7BJm2eV25","messageID":"msg_d7bc8838e001blADQCbz8sjLEY","sessionID":"ses_284395a09ffepHaNJXO7NKvW6E","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_26ffad6fedf7410c8c820657","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-042 — Docusaurus 文档站框架 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** docs\n> **Language:** TypeScript\n> **Size:** M\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `docs/design.md`, `changes/AR-042/design.md`\n\n---\n\n## T1. 初始化 Docusaurus 项目骨架\n\n- [ ] 1.1 在 `docs/` 目录创建 `package.json`，声明依赖：\n  - `@docusaurus/core ^3.7.0`\n  - `@docusaurus/preset-classic ^3.7.0`\n  - `@docusaurus/module-type-aliases ^3.7.0`\n  - `@docusaurus/tsconfig ^3.7.0`\n  - `@docusaurus/types ^3.7.0`\n  - `@mdx-js/react ^3.0.0`\n  - `clsx ^2.0.0`\n  - `prism-react-renderer ^2.3.0`\n  - `react ^19.0.0`\n  - `react-dom ^19.0.0`\n- [ ] 1.2 创建 `babel.config.js`（Docusaurus 默认配置）\n- [ ] 1.3 创建 `tsconfig.json`，继承 `@docusaurus/tsconfig`\n- [ ] 1.4 创建 `docusaurus.config.ts`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.1）：\n  - 站点元信息（title, tagline, favicon, url, baseUrl）\n  - i18n 配置（en/zh）\n  - classic preset（docs, blog, theme）\n  - themeConfig（navbar, footer, prism, algolia placeholder）\n  - Mermaid 支持（`markdown.mermaid: true`, `themes: ['@docusaurus/theme-mermaid']`）\n  - 严格模式（`onBrokenLinks: 'throw'`, `onBrokenAssets: 'throw'`）\n- [ ] 1.5 创建 `sidebars.ts`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.2），定义 7 个分类：\n  - Getting Started, Architecture, User Guide, API Reference, Integrations, Operations, Contributing\n- [ ] 1.6 运行 `npm install` 确认依赖安装成功\n\n**Verification:** `cd docs && npx docusaurus --version` 输出 3.x；`npx tsc --noEmit` 无类型错误\n\n---\n\n## T2. 创建目录结构与分类元数据\n\n- [ ] 2.1 创建 `docs/docs/` 目录结构（参考 `docs/design.md` §1.5）：\n  - `getting-started/`（installation, quick-start, configuration）\n  - `architecture/`（overview, components, session-routing, sandbox-lifecycle）\n  - `user-guide/`（code-interpreter, agent-runtime, cli, python-sdk）\n  - `api-reference/`（control-plane, data-plane, crds）\n  - `integrations/`（dify-plugin, langchain）\n  - `operations/`（deployment, monitoring, troubleshooting, security）\n  - `contributing/`（development, testing, release-process）\n- [ ] 2.2 为每个分类目录创建 `_category_.json`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.3）\n- [ ] 2.3 创建 `docs/src/css/custom.css`（AgentCube 品牌色覆盖）\n- [ ] 2.4 创建 `docs/src/pages/index.tsx`（首页骨架）\n- [ ] 2.5 创建 `docs/src/pages/index.module.css`（首页样式）\n- [ ] 2.6 创建 `docs/src/components/HomepageFeatures/`（首页特性组件）\n- [ ] 2.7 创建 `docs/img/` 目录，放置 logo.svg 和 favicon.ico 占位文件\n\n**Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功，无 broken links/assets 错误\n\n---\n\n## T3. 编写 P0 核心文档内容\n\n- [ ] 3.1 编写 `docs/docs/intro.md`（项目概述，从 `project.md` 迁移）\n- [ ] 3.2 编写 `docs/docs/getting-started/installation.md`（Helm 安装指南）\n- [ ] 3.3 编写 `docs/docs/getting-started/quick-start.md`（5 分钟快速上手）\n- [ ] 3.4 编写 `docs/docs/architecture/overview.md`（系统架构概览，含 Mermaid 图）\n- [ ] 3.5 编写 `docs/docs/user-guide/code-interpreter.md`（Code Interpreter 使用指南）\n- [ ] 3.6 编写 `docs/docs/user-guide/agent-runtime.md`（Agent Runtime 使用指南）\n\n**Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功；所有 P0 文档可通过 `npm run serve` 本地预览\n\n---\n\n## T4. 编写 P1 文档内容与 API 骨架\n\n- [ ] 4.1 编写 `docs/docs/getting-started/configuration.md`（Helm values 参考）\n- [ ] 4.2 编写 `docs/docs/architecture/components.md`（组件详解）\n- [ ] 4.3 编写 `docs/docs/architecture/session-routing.md`（路由与会话管理）\n- [ ] 4.4 编写 `docs/docs/architecture/sandbox-lifecycle.md`（沙箱生命周期）\n- [ ] 4.5 编写 `docs/docs/user-guide/cli.md`（CLI 命令参考）\n- [ ] 4.6 编写 `docs/docs/user-guide/python-sdk.md`（Python SDK 参考）\n- [ ] 4.7 创建 `docs/docs/api-reference/control-plane.md`（API 骨架）\n- [ ] 4.8 创建 `docs/docs/api-reference/data-plane.md`（API 骨架）\n- [ ] 4.9 创建 `docs/docs/api-reference/crds.md`（CRD 参考骨架）\n- [ ] 4.10 编写 `docs/docs/operations/deployment.md`（生产部署指南）\n- [ ] 4.11 编写 `docs/docs/operations/troubleshooting.md`（常见问题排查）\n- [ ] 4.12 编写 `docs/docs/operations/security.md`（认证、RBAC、网络策略）\n- [ ] 4.13 编写 `docs/docs/contributing/development.md`（开发指南）\n- [ ] 4.14 编写 `docs/docs/contributing/testing.md`（测试指南）\n- [ ] 4.15 编写 `docs/docs/contributing/release-process.md`（发布流程）\n- [ ] 4.16 创建 `docs/docs/integrations/dify-plugin.md`（骨架）\n- [ ] 4.17 创建 `docs/docs/integrations/langchain.md`（骨架）\n- [ ] 4.18 创建 `docs/docs/operations/monitoring.md`（骨架）\n\n**Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功；所有文档 frontmatter 符合 schema（§2.4）\n\n---\n\n## T5. 自定义 MDX 组件\n\n- [ ] 5.1 创建 `docs/src/components/ApiEndpoint/index.tsx`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.5）：\n  - Props: `method`, `path`, `description`, `auth`\n  - 渲染 HTTP 方法徽章 + 路径 + 描述\n- [ ] 5.2 创建 `docs/src/components/K8sResource/index.tsx`（参考 `docs/design.md` §2.5）：\n  - Props: `group`, `version`, `kind`, `scope`, `yamlExample`\n  - 渲染 CRD 信息卡片 + 可选 YAML 示例代码块\n- [ ] 5.3 为两个组件编写基础样式（CSS modules 或内联样式）\n- [ ] 5.4 在至少一个文档中使用 `ApiEndpoint` 组件验证渲染\n- [ ] 5.5 在至少一个文档中使用 `K8sResource` 组件验证渲染\n\n**Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功；MDX 组件在 `npm run serve` 中正确渲染\n\n---\n\n## T6. i18n 多语言支持\n\n- [ ] 6.1 运行 `docusaurus write-translations --locale zh` 生成翻译基础文件\n- [ ] 6.2 创建 `docs/i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current.json`（分类/标签翻译）\n- [ ] 6.3 创建 `docs/i18n/zh/docusaurus-theme-classic/navbar.json`（导航栏翻译）\n- [ ] 6.4 创建 `docs/i18n/zh/docusaurus-theme-classic/footer.json`（页脚翻译）\n- [ ] 6.5 创建 `docs/i18n/zh/code.json`（UI 字符串翻译）\n- [ ] 6.6 翻译 P0 文档至中文：\n  - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/intro.md`\n  - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/getting-started/installation.md`\n  - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/getting-started/quick-start.md`\n  - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/architecture/overview.md`\n  - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/user-guide/code-interpreter.md`\n  - `i18n/zh/docusaurus-plugin-content-docs/current/user-guide/agent-runtime.md`\n- [ ] 6.7 创建 `scripts/check-i18n.sh`（参考 `docs/design.md` §5.5），检查翻译覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n\n**Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功；访问 `/zh/docs/` 显示中文内容；`bash scripts/check-i18n.sh` 覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n\n---\n\n## T7. CI/CD 流水线与部署\n\n- [ ] 7.1 创建 `.github/workflows/docs.yml`（参考 `docs/design.md` §5.7）：\n  - PR 触发：`docs/**` 路径变更\n  - Node.js 20 环境，npm ci 缓存\n  - `npx tsc --noEmit` 类型检查\n  - `npm run build` 构建验证\n  - 链接检查（`npx check-links`）\n  - i18n 覆盖率检查\n  - 构建产物上传（`actions/upload-pages-artifact`）\n- [ ] 7.2 创建部署 job（`deploy`），仅在 `main` 分支触发：\n  - 使用 `actions/deploy-pages@v4`\n  - 配置 `permissions: pages: write, id-token: write`\n  - 配置 `environment: github-pages`\n- [ ] 7.3 在 `docs/package.json` 中添加 scripts：\n  - `start`: `docusaurus start`\n  - `build`: `docusaurus build`\n  - `serve`: `docusaurus serve`\n  - `deploy`: `docusaurus deploy`\n  - `clear`: `docusaurus clear`\n  - `typecheck`: `tsc --noEmit`\n- [ ] 7.4 创建 `docs/lighthouserc.json`（参考 `docs/design.md` §5.4）\n- [ ] 7.5 在 Makefile 中添加 docs 相关 target：\n  - `make docs-build`: 构建文档站\n  - `docs-serve`: 启动本地开发服务器\n  - `docs-check`: 运行类型检查 + 构建 + 链接检查\n\n**Verification:** PR 修改 `docs/` 下文件触发 CI 并通过所有检查；`make docs-build` 成功\n\n---\n\n## T8. 搜索与版本管理\n\n- [ ] 8.1 安装 `@easyops-cn/docusaurus-search-local ^0.48.0`（本地搜索 fallback）\n- [ ] 8.2 在 `docusaurus.config.ts` 中配置本地搜索插件\n- [ ] 8.3 配置 Algolia DocSearch placeholder（`appId`, `apiKey` 使用 TBD 占位）\n- [ ] 8.4 运行 `docusaurus docs:version 0.1.x` 创建首个版本快照\n- [ ] 8.5 验证 `versions.json` 包含 `[\"current\", \"0.1.x\"]`\n- [ ] 8.6 验证版本切换 dropdown 在 navbar 中正常工作\n- [ ] 8.7 创建 `docs/versioned_sidebars/version-0.1.x-sidebars.json`\n\n**Verification:** `cd docs && npm run build` 成功；本地搜索可用；版本切换正常\n\n---\n\n## T9. 质量门禁与最终验证\n\n- [ ] 9.1 运行 `cd docs && npx tsc --noEmit` 确认无类型错误\n- [ ] 9.2 运行 `cd docs && npm run build` 确认构建成功\n- [ ] 9.3 运行 `cd docs && npm run serve` 手动验证所有页面渲染\n- [ ] 9.4 验证所有 P0/P1 文档内容完整且无 placeholder 文本\n- [ ] 9.5 验证 i18n 翻译覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n- [ ] 9.6 验证 Mermaid 图表在文档中正确渲染\n- [ ] 9.7 验证 MDX 组件（ApiEndpoint, K8sResource）正常渲染\n- [ ] 9.8 验证本地搜索功能正常\n- [ ] 9.9 验证版本切换功能正常\n- [ ] 9.10 验证 CI workflow 文件语法正确（`act -j build --dryrun` 或 GitHub Actions lint）\n- [ ] 9.11 确认 `docs/.gitignore` 排除 `node_modules/`, `build/`, `.docusaurus/`\n\n**Verification:** 以上全部通过；`npm run build` exit code 0；无 broken links/assets 警告\n\n---\n\n## Task Dependencies\n\n```\nT1 (项目骨架) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n  │                                                                          │\n  ▼                                                                          │\nT2 (目录结构) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n  │                                                                          │\n  ├──────────► T3 (P0 文档) ────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n  │                                                                          │\n  ├──────────► T4 (P1 文档 + API 骨架) ─────────────────────────────────────┤\n  │                                                                          │\n  ├──────────► T5 (MDX 组件) ───────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n  │                                                                          │\n  ▼                                                                          │\nT6 (i18n) ←── T3, T4 ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n  │                                                                          │\n  ▼                                                                          │\nT7 (CI/CD) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n  │                                                                          │\n  ▼                                                                          │\nT8 (搜索 + 版本) ←── T2 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n  │                                                                          │\n  ▼                                                                          │\nT9 (质量门禁) ←── T3, T4, T5, T6, T7, T8 ───────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n**Parallel execution:**\n- T3, T4, T5 可在 T2 完成后并行开发\n- T6 需 T3/T4 完成后开始（依赖英文文档）\n- T7 和 T8 可在 T2 完成后并行开发\n- T9 需所有前置任务完成\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n| # | Criterion | Verification Command |\n|---|-----------|---------------------|\n| AC1 | Docusaurus 项目可构建 | `cd docs && npm run build` exit 0 |\n| AC2 | TypeScript 类型检查通过 | `cd docs && npx tsc --noEmit` |\n| AC3 | 7 个文档分类完整 | `sidebars.ts` 包含所有分类 |\n| AC4 | P0 文档内容完整（6 篇） | `docs/docs/` 下文件存在且非空 |\n| AC5 | P1 文档内容完整（13 篇） | `docs/docs/` 下文件存在且非空 |\n| AC6 | 中文翻译覆盖率 ≥ 80% | `bash scripts/check-i18n.sh` |\n| AC7 | Mermaid 图表渲染正常 | `npm run serve` 手动验证 |\n| AC8 | MDX 组件可用 | ApiEndpoint, K8sResource 渲染正常 |\n| AC9 | 本地搜索功能正常 | 搜索框返回结果 |\n| AC10 | 版本切换正常 | 版本 dropdown 可切换 |\n| AC11 | CI pipeline 通过 | PR 触发 docs workflow 全绿 |\n| AC12 | 无 broken links/assets | `npm run build` 无警告 |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-042/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775898306464,"end":1775898306481}}}}
